  "text": "Grafting of the hypocotyls between the WT rootstock and the atipt1;3;5;7 scion, and vice versa, was done 4 days after germination according to the method of Turnbull et al. [CITATION_1] . The plants were then cultured for 3 weeks on MS solidified with 0.3% Phytagel.",
